==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Spelling
<hw>Spell"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
spelling.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Spelling bee</b></col>, <cd>a spelling match.</cd>
<mark>[U.S.]</mark> -- <col><b>Spelling book</b></col>, <cd>a book with
exercises for teaching children to spell; a speller.</cd> --
<col><b>Spelling match</b></col>, <cd>a contest of skill in spelling
words, between two or more persons.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

